
<html>
    <head>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: sans-serif;
                color: black;
                font-size: 17px;
                margin-right: 5%;
                margin-top: 2%;

            }

            .gender-notice {
                color: gray;
                width: 60%;
                padding: 5px;
                max-width: 500px;
            }

            .footer {
                margin-top: 5%
            }

            .hashtag-logo {
                font-size: 18px;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            .organization-name {
                font-size: 20px;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            .social {
                margin: 30px 0;
            }

            .social .social-img {
                max-height: 48px;
                max-width: 48px;
                margin-right: 10px;
            }

            .social .social-link {
                color: #FFB800;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

        </style>
    </head>
    <body>


        {% for paragraph in paragraphs %}
            <p>{{ paragraph | raw }}</p>
        {% endfor %}


        <div class="footer">
            <img src="{{app_url}}/images/nvs-logo-small-email.png"/>

            <div class="organization-name">
                Novosadski volonterski servis
            </div>
            <div class="hashtag-logo">
                #n>s
            </div>


            <div align="horizontal" class="social">

                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/nsvolonterskiservis" class="social-link">
                    <img src="{{app_url}}/images/facebook-large-yellow.png" class="social-img"/>
                </a>

                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/nsvolonterskiservis" class="social-link">
                    <img src="{{app_url}}/images/instagram-large-yellow.png" class="social-img"/>
                </a>

                <a href="#" class="social-link">
                    <img src="{{app_url}}/images/linkedin-large-yellow.png" class="social-img"/>
                </a>

                <a href="#" class="social-link">
                    <img src="{{app_url}}/images/twitter-large-yellow.png" class="social-img"/>
                </a>

            </div>


            <div class="gender-notice">
                Svi izrazi koji se koriste u #n>s tekstovima, dokumentima, email prepiskama i drugim pisanim stvarima u muškom rodu obuhvataju iste izraze u ženskom rodu.
            </div>

        </div>
    </body>
</html>